survey_response.review_text: I believe me and my wife are very lucky to come across Dr Swetha. I have never seen such a genuine and kind doctor with so much patience who explains in detail and answers all your questions, responds back in case of emergencies and provides such a good treatment. We consulted Dr. Swetha when my wife had to undergo D&C. she did the D&C and then we continued consulting her for treatment for next pregnancy. My wife conceived again and Dr Swetha performed regular scans and provided necessary treatment for the baby growth and ensured the baby is delivered. Post delivery my wife had some other general complications but she stood by us patiently and provided us lot of morale support. I am very thankful to Dr. Swetha for giving such wonderful care and treatment to my wife and help us get a miracle baby boy. ** ***** **** **** *** ********** *********** *************** I definitely & strongly recommend Dr Swetha.

Visited Dr.Swetha for my wife.Actually my wife had PCOD issues, still she gave her a treatment in such a way to conceive naturally that was one of the impressive thing.After pregnancy she did'nt  give any unwanted test and medicines.she is such a polite and friendly doctor.you can ask for details and she will respond with patience.She responds for emergencies quickly without any hesitation, and can reach her over a call and message. During this pregnancy my wife got covid, the way she gave treatment was very good, and she even tracked the progress till my wife gets negative.She is such a dedicated and a sincere doctor , treated like a family.I strongly recommend Dr.Swetha.

We have been consulting Doctors since 1 and half year and we were not being treated by any Gynec in a professional way rather personal treatment.  We sensed a very polite and humble way of treating and addressing our concerns with respect to my Wife's pre-maternal issues and post-delivery counselling and care by Mrs. Dr. Vanamala Swetha garu ( Madhu's Mother Clinic, Nizampet, Hyderabad) . It is an honor to portrait our happiness and over all experience with the journey of my Child from the day of my wife's pregnancy. My wife is strongly recommending this doctor to our friends who has been suffering from different Gynec issues. Before we end this up, out of our experience we assure you will sense our Mother care and safe hands while she treats us.

I first visited Dr.Swetha one and a half year ago for PCOD treatment and was extremely satisfied with how she has explained the problem and made me comfortable with the medical treatment I was given. Since then, from the fertilization treatment to the birth of my child, she has paid utmost care personally to the treatment throughout and I never had to second guess my choice of doctor. She has never rushed a consultation session and would only let me leave until all my questions are answered and I'm comfortable. Overall it was a great experience visiting her and would highly recommend her for anyone looking for a reliable gynecologist/obstetrician.

We would never forget the mental support and care she gave us. We are very fortunate to be under her guidance and medical supervision till date.

review_reply.reply_text: Now era is Early diagnosis ... Early scan is done to Rule out ectopic pregnancy (pregnancy not in uterus ) even though rare it is significant dangerous to mother .I ask for scan at 5weeks ..Gestation sac is seen at 4weeks from which we can confirm pregnancy is in uterus . and even if sac not seen 10days after first scan ,I start investigating for ectopic pregnancy .And I assess need for hormonal support too ...And I do only after your consent ..and in my practice I never charged for repeat scan ...I would have been happy if you asked same query during consultation instead of giving wrong statements in online platform...
